Package gov.nih.nci.hl7.ui.hsm.wizard

This package defines all related UI navigation classes to support functionalities regarding to HL7 V3 specification.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AssociationListFrontPage Define clone list in the check box format to allow user to pick.
AssociationListWizard Handles the selection of HL7 V3 association list.
NewHSMFrontPage Define the first page in the open wizard.
NewHSMWizard Handles the selection of HL7 V3 type and file source.
